Text: there's something wrong with TPB,it takes days or even weeks to download a single movie,start SEEDING arseholes!!!!!!!!

Oh, shut up! You have uploaded nothing, so just shut the **** up! To upload 5GiB and get enough seeds for the torrent to sustain itself can take days, weeks or even months if the subject of the torrent isn't very popular.

And some uploaders also like to download, and seed back what they download, so their upload-bandwidth isn't fully on uploading THEIR torrent, but also other people's torrents. So I say again: Until you have uploaded something yourself, and seen how long it takes, SHUT THE **** UP AND ENJOY THE FACT THAT SOME PEOPLE ACTUALLY BOTHERS TO SHARE THIS WITH YOU!!
